collectionMetadata.name: 3G Public Cellular Mobile Telephone Services - Average Drop Call Rate
collectionMetadata.description: This indicator measures the percentage of unintended disconnection of 3G mobile calls by the cellular network during a 100 second call. Under IDA's 3G PCMTS QoS framework, mobile operators are required to achieve <1% drop call rate (average across the entire month).

datasetMetadata.name: 3G Public Cellular Mobile Telephone Services - Average Drop Call Rate
